105
106const HAL_RATE_TABLE *
107ar5416GetRateTable(struct ath_hal *ah, u_int mode)
108{
109 HAL_RATE_TABLE *rt;
110 switch (mode) {
111 case HAL_MODE_11NG_HT20:
112 case HAL_MODE_11NG_HT40PLUS:
113 case HAL_MODE_11NG_HT40MINUS:
114 rt = &ar5416_11ng_table;
115 break;
116 case HAL_MODE_11NA_HT20:
117 case HAL_MODE_11NA_HT40PLUS:
118 case HAL_MODE_11NA_HT40MINUS:
119 rt = &ar5416_11na_table;
120 break;
121 default:
122 return ar5212GetRateTable(ah, mode);
123 }
124 ath_hal_setupratetable(ah, rt);
125 return rt;
126}
